- `toUpperCase()` — ensures all letters are uppercase.
- `substring(0, 5)` — limits the input to 5 characters.
- `$input[0].selectionStart` — gets the current cursor position.
- `$input[0].setSelectionRange(cursorPos, cursorPos)` — restores the cursor to the same position after the input is modified.

